revision.text:
The '''Shard Trader''' is an [[NPCs|NPC]] in Pok√©clicker. There are multiple shops in each [[Regions|Region]]. Shard Traders sell [[Eggs]] and/or [[Evolution Items]], that are purchasable with a combination of [[Shards]] and [[Quest Points]] {{Questpoints}}.

